@startuml
title Activity Diagram - AI Enhancement for Education

start
:Applicant requests education enhancement;
:Frontend sends POST /api/profile/ai-enhance/education with Bearer token;
:Server validates JWT token;
:Server validates description, degree, and institution;
if (Validation successful?) then (yes)
  :Send request to Gemini AI with education details;
  :Gemini AI generates enhanced education text;
  :Server receives enhanced text;
  :Send 200 response with enhancedText;
  :Frontend displays suggestion to applicant;
else (no)
  :Return 400 validation error;
  :Display error message;
endif
stop

@enduml
